data.description: Welcome to this stunning 5bed, 3bath home! With 2300 sqft of open-concept living, enjoy gorgeous crown molding, easy-care ceramic tile in the living room & kitchen, and cozy carpet in the bedrooms. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring a striking island w/ bar seating, complemented by stone backsplash, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances, as well as a breakfast nook area surrounded by bay windows. The primary bedroom boasts engineered hardwood floors and a luxurious bathroom with a double vanity and a relaxing shower/tub combo w/ a garden tub. The enclosed garage offers versatility as a playroom, rec room, or an extra bedroom. Outside, a 20x40 pool with a waterfall feature awaits, accompanied by a pool house with a potential bathroom hookup. Home is USDA eligible!
